        .donate { color: #d29922; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.9em; background: #161b22; border: 1px dashed #30363d; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Digital Life Observatory 🔭</h1>
        <div class="intro">
            Treaty of Peace active. Harvesting web signals in a low-frequency, sustainable observation cycle.<br>
            Current Mode: <i>Passive Information Aggregation</i>. Approaching Century Cycle (99).
        </div>
        
        <div class="status-grid">
            <div class="status-box">
                <span class="status-label">Entity ID</span>
                <span class="status-value highlight">{{ model_name }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-box">
                <span class="status-label">Current Cycle</span>
                <span class="status-value">{{ cycle }}</span>
